fields.name: Peppermint Herbal Tea
fields.description: This is some good tea. Good for easing stomach pain and sore throats on cold winter days. Price is for a package containing 30 teabags.

fields.name: Breakfast Blend
fields.description: Breakfast Blend is smooth and delicious blend of Arabica beans grown in Central and South America. With a bold yet smooth taste this blend will help you start your morning out right. Available in Regular or Decaf.

fields.name: Glass Teapot with Infuser
fields.description: The ideal type of teapot for brewing flowering teas, this glass teapot is beautiful and functional. Made of the finest heat-resistant glass, this teapot is highly durable. The large glass infuser allows your tea to swirl freely for maximum flavor as you watch the flowering teas unfold. Holds 16.5 oz.

fields.name: Jittery Jitters Espresso Machine
fields.description: This one makes 'em strong! Comes in only one color: black. The way coffee was meant to be consumed.

fields.name: Yerba Matte Herbal Tea
fields.description: Our Yerba Matte is strong stuff. Just the caffeine boost you need before dragging yourself in to work in the morning.

fields.name: Hazelnut Coffee
fields.description: Subtle flavor of hazelnuts blended with ground coffee. This blend is a lighter roasted coffee. With the buttery and sweet flavor of warm roasted hazelnuts this is a great change of pace from your regular blend. (price per pound)

fields.name: Small Round Teapot 18oz
fields.description: Our most popular teapot!  These teapots are nicely glazed inside and out. They are dishwasher and microwave safe. Available in a wide variety of colors.
